      "### Nyströmformer's Approximation Complexity\n",
      "\n",
      "The Nyströmformer approximates the attention matrix $A \\approx C A_k^{-1} R$, where:\n",
      "*   $C$ is an $N \\times m$ matrix (e.g., $Q K_m^T$, where $K_m$ are the landmark keys).\n",
      "*   $R$ is an $m \\times N$ matrix (e.g., $Q_m K^T$, where $Q_m$ are the landmark queries).\n",
      "*   $A_k$ is an $m \\times m$ matrix (e.g., $Q_m K_m^T$).\n",
      "\n",
      "The core operations involve:\n",
      "1.  **Computing landmark-to-all and all-to-landmark attention scores:**\n",
      "    *   $Q K_m^T$ (size $N \\times m$): $O(N m D)$\n",
      "    *   $Q_m K^T$ (size $m \\times N$): $O(N m D)$\n",
      "    *   $Q_m K_m^T$ (size $m \\times m$): $O(m^2 D)$\n",
      "2.  **Inverting the landmark-to-landmark attention matrix:**\n",
      "    *   $(Q_m K_m^T)^{-1}$ (size $m \\times m$): $O(m^3)$\n",
      "3.  **Combining these matrices and multiplying by V:**\n",
