      "5.  **Managing Out-of-Vocabulary (OOV) Words:** For subword tokenizers (like BPE, WordPiece), it helps break down unknown words into known subword units, mitigating the OOV problem.\n",
      "\n",
      "In essence, tokenization is the foundational first step that transforms human-readable text into a format that can be understood and processed by computational NLP systems.\n",
      "True answer: To translate text into data that can be processed by the model.\n"
